onstrate\nthat our learned policy outperforms existing state-of-the-art MAF algorithms in\na set of experiments that vary team size, number and placement of resources,\nand key environmental dynamics not seen at training time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jun 2020 06:13:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 16 May 2021 16:41:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2021 02:36:22 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 13 Feb 2022 04:09:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
