e entropy classes is conducted. Through this\nstudy, two original phenomena, referred to as shear-to-entropy and\nentropy-to-shear transfers, are highlighted and confirmed on standard\ntwo-dimensional test cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jun 2020 15:26:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-16"}
